steps.html_instructions: Head southwest on S Euclid Ave toward E Pleasant Dr
S Euclid Ave turns right and becomes E Pleasant Dr

Take the 1st right onto US-83 S/W Sioux Ave
Continue to follow US-83 S
Turn right to merge onto I-90 W/US-83 S
Take exit 192 for US-83 S/I-90 toward White River

Turn left onto I-90BUS E/US-83 S
Continue to follow US-83 S

Turn right onto US-83 S/Adams St
Continue to follow US-83 S
Entering Nebraska

Turn left onto US-20 E/US-83 S/E C St
Continue to follow US-20 E/US-83 S

Turn right onto NE-2 W/US-83
Continue to follow US-83

Keep left at the fork to continue on I-76 W, follow signs for Interstate 76/Denver
Entering Colorado

Turn left onto I-76 Business/US-34/US-6 E (signs for CO-71)
Continue to follow I-76 Business/US-34

Turn right onto Hwy 160 Bypass/160 Hwy Bypass
Continue to follow 160 Hwy Bypass

Turn left to merge onto I-25 S
Entering New Mexico
Turn right onto NM-466 N/Old Pecos Trail (signs for Historic US 66)
